---
---
<section class="relative bg-ink px-5 py-20 md:px-8 md:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
    <span class="kicker"><span data-i18n="es">por qué duke</span><span data-i18n="en">why duke</span></span>
    <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-cream md:text-5xl">
      <span data-i18n="es">BUENA COMIDA. BUENAS COPAS. BUENAS NOCHES.</span>
      <span data-i18n="en">GOOD FOOD. GOOD DRINKS. GOOD NIGHTS.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="feature-card-dark">
        <div class="feature-icon-dark">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M4 10h16M3 14h18a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2zM6 10a6 4 0 0 1 12 0" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-cream">
          <span data-i18n="es">Simple o doble</span><span data-i18n="en">Single or double</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 font-body text-sm text-stone">
          <span data-i18n="es">Combinaciones cargadas y opciones dobles para el que tiene hambre de verdad.</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">Loaded combinations and double options for real appetite.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card-dark">
        <div class="feature-icon-dark">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M5 3h14l-6 9v7h-2v-7z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-cream">
          <span data-i18n="es">Cócteles y smoothies</span><span data-i18n="en">Cocktails & smoothies</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 font-body text-sm text-stone">
          <span data-i18n="es">Barra completa con tres cervezas de barril, cócteles de autor y smoothies cremosos.</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">Full bar with three beers on draft, signature cocktails and creamy smoothies.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card-dark">
        <div class="feature-icon-dark">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-cream">
          <span data-i18n="es">Música en vivo</span><span data-i18n="en">Live music</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 font-body text-sm text-stone">
          <span data-i18n="es">Noches de música en vivo los viernes que convierten la cena en una experiencia de club.</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">Friday live music nights that turn dinner into a club experience.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
